  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELCOME TO ASCII-RIFT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ASCII-RIFT is a fast, reactive, music-driven game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hazards are generated from the music itself.<br>If you don’t move with the track — you die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHART MODE</strong><br>Score-focused runs built around the music.<br>The track and lanes intensify with the song.<br>Make it to the end of the track without dying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RIFT MODE</strong><br>Escalating procedural loops for endless play.<br>Level up. Adapt. Reset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No permanent progression — only skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ADDITIONAL INFO</strong><br>Includes <strong>10 original WAV tracks</strong> I created.<br>You can also drop your own <strong>.wav</strong> files into the music folder to generate entirely new runs automatically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring your own soundtrack.<br>Change the battlefield.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELCOME TO ASCII-RIFT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ASCII-RIFT is a fast, reactive, music-driven game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hazards are generated from the music itself.<br>If you don’t move with the track — you die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHART MODE</strong><br>Score-focused runs built around the music.<br>The track and lanes intensify with the song.<br>Make it to the end of the track without dying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RIFT MODE</strong><br>Escalating procedural loops for endless play.<br>Level up. Adapt. Reset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No permanent progression — only skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ADDITIONAL INFO</strong><br>Includes <strong>10 original WAV tracks</strong> I created.<br>You can also drop your own <strong>.wav</strong> files into the music folder to generate entirely new runs automatically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring your own soundtrack.<br>Change the battlefield.</p>",
